data.description: THIS HOME HAS A LOT TO OFFER!  Pueblo West Ranch Home on almost 1/2 acre with amazing views and PAID OFF solar panels! Main level features a primary bedroom, 2 additional bedrooms, an open living room with wood floors, a spacious kitchen with tile floors, solid surface countertops and plenty of cabinet space. Eating area walks out to a private, HUGE, fully fenced back yard which backs to equestrian trails.  Full finished basement features a large Family Room/Rec Room perfect for entertaining, 2 bedrooms, bath and storage area with lots of cabinets. A Tankless water heater is found in the laundry room! Sprinkler system in front lawn. Pueblo West offers plenty of outdoor attractions and recreation including Lake Pueblo State Park's camping, fishing, hiking, biking and outdoor spaces.
